reviewText: ... but man! Are these celebrity roasts FUNNY! Also recommended is Dean Martin Celebrity Roasts 7 DVD Collector's Edition(15 roasts). Wet your pants FUNNY! Don Rickles fan? He's in 20 of these... chances ARE...
